cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.AI

The paper discusses a tool for testing the correctness and completeness of provenance capture tools, which is relevant to computer security (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), programming languages (cs.PL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as provenance is used in machine learning and data mining. However, since the paper focuses on testing and comparing the expressiveness of provenance systems, cs.CR and cs.DB are the most likely categories.
